SWITCH(
  TRUE(),
  Fact_Jobs[Remote_Ratio] = 100, "Remote",
   Fact_Jobs[Remote_Ratio] >= 50, "Mostly Remote / Hybrid",
   Fact_Jobs[Remote_Ratio] > 0, "Hybrid",
   Fact_Jobs[Remote_Ratio] = 0, "On-site",
  "Unknown"
)
